    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Detection of cryptic taxa in Leptobrachium nigrops (Amphibia, Anura, Megophryidae), with description of two new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281823>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281818> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281823>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Spectrograms (above) and wave form (below) of advertisement call of (A) L. nigrops (KUHE 15430) from Kuala Lumpur, Malay Peninsula and (B) L. ingeri sp. nov. (KUHE 53834) from Santubong, Sarawak." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281823/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.281818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map of Malaysia and western part of Indonesia, showing sample localities of the L. nigrops group that are used in the molecular analyses (triangle) and morphological analyses (reversed triangle). Blue: L. nigrops. Yellow: L. ingeri sp. nov. Red: L. kanowitense sp. nov.). Details of localities are shown in Table 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/281818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

